{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The chatbot follows a simple flow cycle. There are a couple of questions. Each question is for collecting data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"we need to create a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/Booking"},{"type":"text","text":". A Booking is for a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/Guest"},{"type":"text","text":" and the Guest needs one or more "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/Room"},{"type":"text","text":"s."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"That is we first ask the user for its firstname and lastname. With these attributes we can create a first but"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"not complete Guest object. Than we ask for some dates for the Booking. With the dates we check if a room is available."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If the are available they are put to the Booking object and at the end the user is asked for a mail address. This is the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"last information to complete the Guest object. The user is asked for a confirmation and in the positive case we store"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the Guest and the Booking object into the database."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here you can see the workflow:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"ChatbotWorkflow.svg"}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/hotelchatbot\/chatbotworkflow"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/ChatbotWorkflow","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This article describes how the chatbot works."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"ChatbotWorkflow","role":"collectionGroup","modules":[{"name":"HotelChatBot"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/DatabaseStructure","doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/tutorials\/HotelChatBot\/HowToAdjust","doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/tutorials\/HotelChatBot\/RetrainModels"],"generated":true}],"references":{"doc://org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot/documentation/HotelChatBot/Room":{"role":"symbol","title":"Room","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Room"}],"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/Room","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Room"}],"url":"\/documentation\/hotelchatbot\/room"},"doc://org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot/tutorials/HotelChatBot/RetrainModels":{"role":"project","title":"What to do for improving the quality of the chatbot","estimatedTime":"10min","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A good ML model is trained from a large set of samples. So a developer is not able to create such a hugh"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set. For this the app collects all the user input and creates training and testfiles when the app will terminate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The disandvantage is that the end of the program is slow with a big set of data but this is only for the POC."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In a real world you have that in the background system and the user does not recognize that."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The created files can be used for retrain the models."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/tutorials\/HotelChatBot\/RetrainModels","kind":"project","type":"topic","url":"\/tutorials\/hotelchatbot\/retrainmodels"},"doc://org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot/tutorials/HotelChatBot/HowToAdjust":{"role":"project","title":"Essential steps for adjusting the chatbot.","estimatedTime":"10min","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The following steps describe what need to do to improve the chatbot and to adjust it to own needs"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There are the following steps necessary:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/tutorials\/HotelChatBot\/HowToAdjust","kind":"project","type":"topic","url":"\/tutorials\/hotelchatbot\/howtoadjust"},"doc://org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot/documentation/HotelChatBot/DatabaseStructure":{"role":"collectionGroup","title":"DatabaseStructure","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This article describes the database in a class diagram."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/DatabaseStructure","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/hotelchatbot\/databasestructure"},"ChatbotWorkflow.svg":{"alt":"Flowchart of the chatbot main process","type":"image","identifier":"ChatbotWorkflow.svg","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/ChatbotWorkflow.svg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot/documentation/HotelChatBot/Guest":{"role":"symbol","title":"Guest","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Guest"}],"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/Guest","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Guest"}],"url":"\/documentation\/hotelchatbot\/guest"},"doc://org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot/documentation/HotelChatBot/Booking":{"role":"symbol","title":"Booking","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Booking"}],"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot\/Booking","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Booking"}],"url":"\/documentation\/hotelchatbot\/booking"},"doc://org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot/documentation/HotelChatBot":{"role":"collection","title":"HotelChatBot","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This chatbot is a proof of concept how a chat bot can build up as a Mac OS app with the Apple development included tools for machine learning."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.luenstedt.HotelChatBot\/documentation\/HotelChatBot","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/hotelchatbot"}}}